---
title: Grilled Italian Sausage Cheeseburger with Foil-Pouch Peppers and Arugula Salad
description: This grilled sausage burger is the new hot dish in town. Italian and garlic-spiced pork is topped with marinara and grilled veggies, then sandwiched between toasted buns! A beautifully dressed bright salad is the perfect pairing for this heavy-hitter.
